title: Take a stroll over to the Outlet Malls
posting_body: ['Text 6325A  for more info!', 'Are you ready to make your move into a new home?', ' I’d like to help!', ' As a native Austinite, with 10 years of experience in the rental housing market, I know how to help you in the most efficient and productive way.', ' I have access to thousands of apartments, condos and houses, including the private market.', 'I will not send you random properties, that may or may not be a good fit and that may or may not have anything available.', ' I will send you direct links to the actual property, with up-to-date availability, pricing and floor plans.', ' Once you decide on the properties that are a good fit for you, I will map out a plan and schedule tours, on your behalf, for each individual property.', 'Let me do the work and all you have to do is point and click and show up for the appointment.', 'How do I get paid for my services, you may ask?', ' I get paid by the management company that you choose to lease from.', ' My services are free to you!', ' All that is needed is that you write my name down, on the application, as the referring agent that help you.', 'Disclaimer:  I do not service short term housing.', ' You will have to call the property directly to ask for corporate housing or short-term rental options.', 'Must have excellent rental history, no criminal background record and valid bank records or an offer letter to validate income of three times the rent.', ' Credit scores don’t need to be perfect, as long as you don’t owe any properties money.', 'I look forward to helping you make your home search an easy success!', 'Experience a new level of comfort in a community that offers the whole package: remodeled interiors, upgraded amenities, and a great location on Old Settlers Boulevard.', 'Nestled under an inviting canopy of oak trees, Terrace Apartments promotes a sense of calm.', 'The six floor plans of our Round Rock, TX, apartments are open and expansive, having the look and feel of a single-family home.', 'The on-site features extend your private living space outdoors, and the proximity to local employers and reputed schools makes the whole experience convenient.', 'Our apartments in Round Rock span between 777 and 1,350 square feet to ensure you have enough room to move around.', 'These spacious designs are further portrayed in the large kitchens, generously sized living rooms, and expansive closets.', 'Add in designer interior finishes, including high-gloss countertops and vinyl plank floorings, and your one, two, or three-bedroom apartment is both practical and stylish.', 'Outside your home, youll discover a thoughtful list of features meant to enhance home comforts.', 'Youll find a beautiful swimming pool and spa, a well-equipped fitness studio, along with picnic and grilling stations.', 'We took care of our furry residents, too, by adding a pet park and pet wash station to our amenity list.', 'Terraces location provides an energized lifestyle near the many business and shopping centers in Round Rocks central economic hub.', 'Your Round Rock apartment is less than 10 minutes away from Dells corporate headquarters, Baylor Scott & White, and Amazons distribution center.', 'Add in the fast access to Round Rock Premium Outlet Mall, and you have it all.', 'Embrace the good life: discover which floor plan is the best for you and your household today!']
